---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import HeroText from '~/components/widgets/HeroText.astro';

const metadata = { title: 'Privacy Policy | SSS Health Solutions' };
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <HeroText title="Privacy Policy" />
  <section class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-4xl lg:py-20">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert dark:text-slate-400">
      <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> March 2026</p>
      
      <p>SSS Health Solutions LLC ("we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit our website or request our insurance advisory services.</p>

      <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>We collect information that you voluntarily provide to us via our online contact forms (powered by Web3Forms), including but not limited to: your full name, email address, phone number, and basic demographic or health information required strictly for the purpose of generating accurate health insurance quotes.</p>

      <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <p>Your information is used exclusively to:<br>
      • Provide you with requested health insurance quotes and advisory services.<br>
      • Communicate with you via phone, email, or SMS regarding your inquiry.<br>
      • Submit necessary applications to selected insurance carriers upon your explicit approval.</p>

      <h3>3. TCPA & SMS Communication Consent</h3>
      <p>By providing your phone number and submitting a form on this website, you provide your electronic signature and express written consent to be contacted by SSS Health Solutions LLC (and its licensed agents) via phone calls and SMS/text messages, even if your number is on a Do Not Call list. Standard message and data rates may apply. You may opt-out of SMS communications at any time by replying "STOP".</p>

      <h3>4. No Sale of Personal Data</h3>
      <p><strong>We do not sell, rent, or lease your personal data or lead information to third-party marketers or other agencies.</strong> Your information is only shared with specific, highly-rated insurance carriers (e.g., UnitedHealthcare) strictly for the purpose of underwriting and policy issuance.</p>

      <h3>5. Data Security</h3>
      <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. However, no transmission of data over the internet is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of data sent through our site.</p>

      <h3>6. Contact Us</h3>
      <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to request the deletion of your data, please contact us directly through our website's Contact page.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
